01:48:34.000 --> 01:48:35.999
[They imitate Bamby cutting off the line to restart]

01:48:36.000 --> 01:48:37.999
[They repeat the clipped restart]

01:48:38.000 --> 01:48:38.999
[They repeat it again]

01:48:39.000 --> 01:48:39.999
