01:48:40.000 --> 01:48:40.999
[He repeats the troublesome syllable]

01:48:41.000 --> 01:48:42.999
If I don't keep doing it, my pitch drops.

01:48:43.000 --> 01:48:43.999
This is so funny.

01:48:44.000 --> 01:48:44.999
To keep the path in place?

01:48:45.000 --> 01:48:45.999
I have to maintain the path.

01:48:46.000 --> 01:48:48.999
To keep it, I need to stay right here.

01:48:49.000 --> 01:48:52.999
-All of you, seriously...
-I'm dying. This is hilarious.

01:48:53.000 --> 01:48:53.999
My cheeks hurt from laughing.

01:48:54.000 --> 01:48:55.999
Yes.

01:48:56.000 --> 01:48:56.999
It became another good memory.

01:48:57.000 --> 01:48:58.999
-We made another memory.
-It's a memory once it's over.

01:48:59.000 --> 01:48:59.999
We made a memory.

01:49:00.000 --> 01:49:00.999
Everything becomes a memory afterward.

01:49:01.000 --> 01:49:01.999
Right. And the song turned out so well.

01:49:02.000 --> 01:49:02.999
Ah.

01:49:03.000 --> 01:49:03.999
Great.

